Class Vision

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.usfirst.frc.team1710.robot.Vision

  • public class Vision
extends java.lang.Object
    Author:
    Penn creates variables for a table from limelight creates entries for tx value, ty value and tv value The whole vision class takes the values from limelight and makes the robot spin until it sees the cube, then it drives forward to intake the cube all at the push of a button
